README for Sys::RunUntil

Provide a simple way to make sure the script from which this module is
loaded, is running only for the given (wallclock) time.

Copyright (c) 2005, 2012 Elizabeth Mattijsen <liz@dijkmat.nl>. All rights
reserved.  This program is free software; you can redistribute it and/or
modify it under the same terms as Perl itself.

Required Modules:
 (none)

Version:
 0.04

perl Makefile.PL
make
make test
make install
